reviewText: This video is able to catch some auspcious moments of healing with the horse. I learned alot through this video which lead me to take a class with Anna & both were worth every dollar spent.
I purchased Anna's animal communication cd's and then the Reiki DVD's. Anna's sense and ability to talk people through the process is excellent. My ability to heal others is growing so fast!

Annie is a master of communications with people and animals;  a compassionate an instructive healer !
A must for horse owners.
